{"tid":2047921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗：反對國安法就是違反基本法 應被取消資格","createTime":"2020-06-02T12:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T16:26:26.000Z","uid":125168,"like":36,"dislike":201,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"5cdd9700820fcc289fa2ec1964b5f40d93024b5f","tid":2047921,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】全國人大常委譚耀宗撰文，指議員和參選人如果反對為國家安全立法，就是違反基本法，應被取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗在《紫荊》雜誌撰文，指要積極引導和號召市民支持及遵守國安法，想參與香港建制的人，無論是議員或參選人，都不應該反對為國家安全立法，他指若這些人提出反對，就是違反基本法，應取消他們的資格。他又提到一定要完善國安法的執行機制，不能讓立法決定成為「無牙老虎」，他說可能很多香港市民會對新設立的國安機構感到陌生和擔心，因此要增加市民對執行機制的理解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/26868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F26868&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=57257401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F26868&h=d77ad736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/26868</a>"},{"pid":"2c5b74a8476204530bab59a546224f34700f842b","tid":2047921,"uid":141668,"like":99,"dislike":3,"score":96,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"投反對票嗰個DQ咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/28/99/7949479.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F28%2F99%2F7949479.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600&h=2c32bb00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"005a4bacb83884caf206e308776230328cd3ebcb","tid":2047921,"uid":125168,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"from中國人：<br />\n<br />\n目前中央政府將只要不跪下做奴才的全都定義為港獨。<br />\n<br />\n等你們全都跪下了，中央政府會將跪的姿勢不正確的定義為港獨。<br />\n<br />\n等你們跪下的姿勢都符合要求了，中央政府會將跪著臉上沒有笑容的定義為港獨。<br />\n<br />\n等你們跪著笑著對時候，中央政府會將心裡沒有全然服從的定義為港獨。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n現在香港人明白什麼是港獨的定義了嗎？"},{"pid":"af26d6de614f5503ac5c05ec8a4bfede3c49c2c5","tid":2047921,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2c5b74a8476204530bab59a546224f34700f842b","tid":2047921,"uid":141668,"like":99,"dislike":3,"score":96,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"投反對票嗰個DQ咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/28/99/7949479.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F28%2F99%2F7949479.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600&h=2c32bb00&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"可能7常委嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f5cc138dab21d23b4803620020b52262e7e34f","tid":2047921,"uid":125168,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"以後立法會投反對票就係犯基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0897d7afda7328f6e80b68054aaf2bb8a8e81c35","tid":2047921,"uid":132587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"訂立國安法就是違反基本法"},{"pid":"256f9d924a15392a8a0d1e4a311ce6035ce5a229","tid":2047921,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\